    <section id="game-introduction">
        <h2>Game Introduction</h2>
        <img style="width:30%" src="~/Content/image/zhenzuan.jpg" alt="" />
        <p>Pokemon Diamond Pearl is a nintendo ds RPG DEVELOPED by GAME FREAK, They are the first games of the fourth generation of the pokemon series, released on September 28, 2006. The game's expansion pack Pokemon Platinum was released on September 13, 2008, and the remastered Pokemon Brilliant Diamond Bright Pearl was released on November 19, 2021.</p>
        <p>As with the previous Pokemon series, the game follows a young Pokemon trainer who trains Pokemon, fights Pokemon, and thwarts the plans of a rival organization. The game includes 107 new Pokemon, a reclassification of physical and special moves, a return to the second-generation day and night system, and an upgrade from the third-generation Pokemon Tournament to the Pokemon Super Tournament. The two versions are independent of each other, but the story is basically the same, and players can play the game independently and exchange limited Pokemon to complete the Pokedex.</p>
