            <p>Boys and girls to choose from at the beginning of the game. The chosen protagonist will embark on a journey through Sinnoh, and those who are not chosen will appear in the game as Dr. Yamanashi's assistant.</p>

            <h3>Dr. Yamanashi</h3>
            <img style="width:10%" src="~/Content/image/shanliboshi.jpg" alt="ʿ" />
            <p>A childhood sweetheart and rival who embarks on an adventure at the same time as the protagonist. He will challenge the protagonist many times during his journey, and will also work with the protagonist to take risks and progress together.</p>

            <h3>Tame</h3>
            <img style="width:10%" src="~/Content/image/axun.jpg" alt="" />
            <p>After a long journey, return to the Sinnoh region to study the Pokemon characters. He is an authority on "Pokemon Evolution" and is known for it.</p>

            <h3>Team Galaxy</h3>
            <img style="width:20%" src="~/Content/image/yinhedui.jpg" alt="" />
            <p>Team Galaxy doesn't just use the captured Pokemon to do bad things, it's said they're also secretly researching at a facility. The yellow "G" is their logo.</p>

